    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[520ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[680ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir in your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
