    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once the potatoes are tender, stir a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) into the pan – this is your <strong>Spanish-style stew</strong></p>",
