    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> herby cod</strong> over the <strong>Spanish-style stew</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and sprinkle over the<strong> crispy chorizo </strong>– this is your<strong> Spanish-style herby cod & crispy chorizo stew</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
